      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="35757455">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ender110/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1496436-9.jpg" alt="夕雾" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35757455/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35757455/" class="">第501页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ender110/" class=" " title="夕雾">夕雾</a>
                (余生皆假期)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35757455">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“可我还是想念家乡那种既阳光灿烂同时又大雨倾盆的天气，有一位不久前从费城来火奴鲁鲁的客人问怎么去J&amp;W商店，结果人家告诉他，‘一直往前走，下第一场大雨的时候往左转。’”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-07-30 00:21</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>“可我还是想念家乡那种既阳光灿烂同时又大雨倾盆的天气，有一位不久前从费城来火奴鲁鲁的客人问怎么去J&amp;W商店，结果人家告诉他，‘一直往前走，下第一场大雨的时候往左转。’”</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

